Status of 1.2.0:
================

Candidate changes:

  * r14643
    Use heap not stack for SVN_STREAM_CHUNK_SIZE buffers.
    Justification:
      Buffers simply too big to put on stack; also, API change.
    Notes:
      Use http://svn.collab.net/repos/svn/branches/1.2.x-r14643 for backport.
    Votes:
